{"tid":1591673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[10.1前瞻] V for Vendetta 放映會","createTime":"2019-09-24T09:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T02:59:47.000Z","uid":187489,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f058b0a031980d6d2f17c6b6b62aee92527c3d6","tid":1591673,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"我地需要喺926 / 930 搞一個全港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">V for Vendetta 放映日</span><br />\n<br />\n感染香港市民<br />\n<br />\n30號又好似太遲，睇完都買唔切面具<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有今晚嘅搞手願意再搞多晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係嘅話可以今晚開始前同完結前宣傳埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3sd0QP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3sd0QP.png&h=6de77af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家記得推多啲行動post上黎呀！！<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好俾鄺俊宇/yellow object嗰啲推走晒！嗰啲for國際media係要靠twitter煲，唔係連登煲</span><br />\n<br />\n我地已經唔敢上前線，冇理由連呢個連登主場都要輸俾啲3毛！<br />\n<br />\n今晚見 全民派傳單</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/io4TaBx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fio4TaBx.jpg&h=300aa6ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38240f0c3f54ac306e38124b02e887ebb281d6d0","tid":1591673,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df2e16e106bb